  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b9a\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0bb5\u0baf\u0bcb\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b89\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb4\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Elderly man dies while waiting in queue for fuel",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "The man died while waiting in line to get fuel at a petrol station in Borallai area of \u200b\u200bColombo.",
        "Due to the recent crisis in the country, people have to wait in queues for days to get fuel and cooking gas.",
        "It is noteworthy that so far 11 people have died while shouting in queues nationwide."
      ],
